title: Average weekly working hours in Sweden 2019 , by type of employment
yAxis: Average number of working hours per week
summary: This bar chart has 4 categories for the x axis representing Form of Employment, and a y axis representing Average number of working hours per week.
The highest category is found at Self-employed where Average number of working hours per week is 35.4.
The lowest category is found at Temporary_employed where Average number of working hours per week is 25.5.
